  "description": "<p><strong>近日，外媒在苹果的供应商责任(Supplier Responsibility)页面上发现，该公司就印尼邦加岛非法采矿问题表达了自己的担忧，同时它还表示公司将会密切关注这一问题并对此展开调查。</strong>据悉，印尼是全球产锡矿量最多的国家之一，不过在近几年来，该地区的采锡矿业多次爆出非法采集的丑闻。这使得从该地区获取锡原料的苹果公司拉紧了神经。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e8b7898/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244399.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E8%A1%A8%E6%98%8E%E7%AB%8B%E5%9C%BA+%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%81%E8%AE%B8%E5%85%B6%E4%BE%9B%E5%BA%94%E5%95%86%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E6%89%8B%E6%AE%B5%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96%E5%8E%9F%E6%96%99\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244399.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E8%A1%A8%E6%98%8E%E7%AB%8B%E5%9C%BA+%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%81%E8%AE%B8%E5%85%B6%E4%BE%9B%E5%BA%94%E5%95%86%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E6%89%8B%E6%AE%B5%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96%E5%8E%9F%E6%96%99\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244399.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E8%A1%A8%E6%98%8E%E7%AB%8B%E5%9C%BA+%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%81%E8%AE%B8%E5%85%B6%E4%BE%9B%E5%BA%94%E5%95%86%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E6%89%8B%E6%AE%B5%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96%E5%8E%9F%E6%96%99\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244399.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E8%A1%A8%E6%98%8E%E7%AB%8B%E5%9C%BA+%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%81%E8%AE%B8%E5%85%B6%E4%BE%9B%E5%BA%94%E5%95%86%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E6%89%8B%E6%AE%B5%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96%E5%8E%9F%E6%9